item.description: score:-36 Chances: In the closing of the recent trading day, Snap (SNAP) stood at $11.45, denoting a +1.24% change from the preceding trading day. nCino (NCNO) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 75% and 0.71%, respectively, for the quarter ended January 2024.
